'''全甲格斗<ref>{{Cite book|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=QBiwFSL5FuoC&q=Lille+behourd&pg=PA334|title=Tournois, joutes, pas d'armes dans les villes de Flandre à la fin du Moyen Age (1300-1486)|last=Neste|first=Evelyne van den|date=1996|publisher=École nationale des chartes|isbn=9782900791158|language=fr|access-date=2021-01-11|archive-date=2021-10-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211020195305/https://books.google.com/books?id=QBiwFSL5FuoC&q=Lille+behourd&pg=PA334}}</ref>'''是一种格斗运动和體育賽事，參賽者必須使用[[中世纪|中世纪]]時期的钢制[[钝器|钝器]]<ref>{{Cite web|title=Historical Medieval Battles. What is it?|url=http://middleagestoday.com/en/node/818|accessdate=2012-11-29|publisher=Middle Ages Today|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121204065806/http://middleagestoday.com/en/node/818|archivedate=2012-12-04}}</ref>以及盔甲和武器進行格鬥。万国之战（Battle of the Nations ）网站規定，全甲格鬥的參賽者的盔甲和武器必须符合真實歷史和以及安全規範<ref>{{Cite web|title=Rules & Regulations {{!}} Battle of the Nations|url=http://botn.info/en-rules-regulations|accessdate=2019-05-25|work=botn.info|archive-date=2019-02-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190227182157/http://botn.info/en-rules-regulations}}</ref>。

選手身穿现代生产的用钢制成的盔甲<ref>{{Cite web|title=First steps in choosing armor {{!}} Battle of the Nations|url=http://botn.info/news/en-first-steps-in-choosing-armor|accessdate=2019-05-25|work=botn.info|archive-date=2020-11-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201126175922/https://botn.info/news/en-first-steps-in-choosing-armor}}</ref>參加格鬥比賽，盔甲盡可能地復原歷史<ref>{{Cite web|title=Armor issue. Documentary sources, credibility and compliance {{!}} Battle of the Nations|url=http://botn.info/news/en-armor-issue-documentary-sources-credibility-and-compliance|accessdate=2019-05-25|work=botn.info|archive-date=2020-10-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201027011539/https://botn.info/news/en-armor-issue-documentary-sources-credibility-and-compliance}}</ref>。在比賽規則下，選手可以攻擊對手身体上的任何部位<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.telegraph.co.uk/men/the-filter/knight-fights-inside-the-strange-and-savage-world-of-medieval-mm/|title=Knight fights: Inside the strange and savage world of medieval MMA|author=Wells|first=Jonathan|date=2016-01-22|work=The Telegraph|accessdate=2019-05-26|language=en-GB|issn=0307-1235|archive-date=2021-01-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210113070700/https://www.telegraph.co.uk/men/the-filter/knight-fights-inside-the-strange-and-savage-world-of-medieval-mm/}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Rules and regulations for Buhurt categories|url=http://botn.info/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/Rules-for-BUHURT-CATEGORIES1_V1-9.pdf|work=Rules and Regulations {{!}} Battle of the Nations|access-date=2021-01-11|archive-date=2021-01-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210110034615/https://botn.info/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/Rules-for-BUHURT-CATEGORIES1_V1-9.pdf}}</ref>。全甲格斗比賽還設有裁判<ref>{{Cite web|title=Marshal Committee|url=http://botn.info/organization-group/en-marshal-committee|accessdate=2019-05-26|work=botn.info|archive-date=2020-11-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201125163008/https://botn.info/organization-group/en-marshal-committee}}</ref>。

